description: But opposition leaders dismiss Alexander Lukashenko's comments as a mere stalling tactic.
title: Belarus protests: Embattled leader Alexander Lukashenko hints he may quit
title_page: Belarus protests: Embattled leader Alexander Lukashenko hints he may quit - BBC News
maintext: So this seems like a nod of consent from Alexander Lukashenko, the BBC's Sarah Rainsford in Moscow says. It looks like a sign that he got the hint, and is ready to map his own path out of power.
